data.description: This is a must see beautiful home. Completely remodeled/upgraded in 2020!  $50k Plus worth of upgrades. Walk into the entry to a large foyer with a grand curved wooded banister.  Enjoy a formal living and dining room as well as open kitchen/family room with spacious eating nook.  The master bedroom ensuite has a dual vanity quartz countertops, separate shower & tub and oversized walk in close with built in's. All bathrooms have been upgraded with new cabinets and quartz counters.  Oversized Den off living area with barn door entrance. The backyard is set for great entertaining with pool & water feature.  Enjoy an extended garage on one side for extra storage. Also, may be available for rent.
